Dear *Elizabeth*
I wish to acknowledge your mail and thank you for your interest to
work/partner with our company and our investor to finance your project.
Our investors(lenders) are from Qatar and Kuwait and they have the
financial capacity to fund/finance any projects up to US$5 Billion U S
Dollars for short or long term loan
Our investors(lenders) funds projects through loan or joint venture
(partnership) as stated in our first message to you and the loans are
granted on viable projects for a minimum of 10 years at an annual interest
of 3% after the grace period of 12 months (one year)
For us to move forward, you are advised to fill in the attached KYC form
and return it with a copy of your project proposal or business plan for our
company/investor review and approval after the due diligence has been
carried out by our legal team.
As soon as the filled KYC form is received with a copy of your project
proposal/business plan,  you will be communicated by the company with
relevant documents/approval of your project funding by our investor and the
loan agreement/contract will be drafted to be signed by both parties and
legalized in court to protect the interest of all parties.
You can know more about our company through our website:
www.tridentfinance.net
Looking forward to hearing from you with the requested information about
your project.
Thank you for your understanding and cooperation
Regards,
  *David Louis*
Investment Consultant/Broker
